ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectLoran-C St. Marys 1977 Termination of Treaty (US) #8
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America constituting an Agreement to provide for the Establishment of an Experimental Loran-C Power Chain in the Vicinity of the St. Marys River in Ontario and Michigan, done on 29 March 1977.
